WEBVTT

00:06:57.615 --> 00:07:01.411
that involves an organized
gathering of people.

00:07:01.435 --> 00:07:05.745
And my new dream is to improve,
adapt and deploy the system

00:07:05.769 --> 00:07:11.238
all over the world to prevent loss of life
and ensure a safe flow of people,

00:07:11.262 --> 00:07:14.049
because every human soul is precious,

00:07:14.073 --> 00:07:16.451
whether at concerts or sporting events,

00:07:16.475 --> 00:07:18.362
the Maha Kumbh Mela in Allahabad,

00:07:18.386 --> 00:07:19.837
the Hajj in Mecca,

00:07:19.861 --> 00:07:21.758
the Shia procession to Karbala

00:07:21.782 --> 00:07:23.266
or at the Vatican City.

00:07:23.893 --> 00:07:25.770
So what do you all think, can we do it?

00:07:25.794 --> 00:07:26.945
(Audience) Yes!

00:07:26.969 --> 00:07:28.120
Thank you.

00:07:28.144 --> 00:07:29.145
(Cheers)

00:07:29.169 --> 00:07:32.439
(Applause)